  "title": "Sales & Business Development Manager [Japanese Speaking]",
  "description": "<p>[Job ID:1398777]<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong> <br /> New Business Development</p><ul><li>Identifying and approaching potential clients.</li><li>Analyzing needs of existing clients.</li><li>Coordinating technology development projects (internal and external).</li></ul><p>Account Management</p><ul><li>Coordinating with end customers, suppliers, and manufacturing plants.</li><li>Handling troubleshooting and issues.</li><li>Forecast management, payment management, etc.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p> [Must]</p><ul><li>Experience in the manufacturing industry or technology-based B2B business (Experience as Sales or Business Development is preferred).</li><li>Understanding of manufacturing or businesses dealing with technical products.</li><li>Ability to think independently and structure tasks.</li><li>Polite and professional demeanor, both internally and externally.</li><li>High motivation to learn about new fields and technologies.</li><li>Proactive attitude (taking initiative rather than waiting for instructions).</li><li>Proficiency in Japanese to communicate with Japanese speaking counterparts. </li></ul><p>[Advantage]</p><ul><li>Experience working for a motor supplier.</li><li>Basic knowledge of motors (especially BLDC motors and pump motors).<br /></li></ul><p>If you are interested in the role, please feel free to contact me at<br /><strong>cv_madoka@goodjobcreations.com.sg</strong></p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Ochi Madoka<br />EA Personnel Registration Number: R24125474<br />EA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
